"title":"Hadith on Disciples: The Prophet&#8217;s disciple is Zubayr ibn &#8216;Awwam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 10, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Verily, every prophet has a disciple, and my disciple is Al-Zubayr ibn al-'Awwam.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3719 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0644\u0650\u0643\u064f\u0644\u0651\u0650 \u0646\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064d \u062d\u064e\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064b\u0627 \u0648\u064e\u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e \u062d\u064e\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0632\u0651\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6104,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/09\/sahabah-first-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":3269,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Companions: First Muslims were slaves, women, Abu Bakr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 9, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ammar reported: I saw the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, while there was no one with him but fives slaves, two women, and Abu Bakr. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3460 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0631 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0623\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0648\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8100,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/13\/prophet-humble-young-servants\/","url_meta":{"origin":3269,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Humility: The Prophet is humble with young servants","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 13, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: Any of the young servant-girls among the people of Medina would take the hand of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and lead him wherever she wished. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6072 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0646\u0633 \u0628\u0646 \u0645\u0627\u0644\u0643 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15155,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/21\/prophet-handsome-red-clothing\/","url_meta":{"origin":3269,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Clothing: The Prophet was handsome, wore red clothing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 21, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bara' ibn 'Azib reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was of moderate height, with broad shoulders and hair that reached to his ears. I once saw him wearing a red mantle and I have not seen anyone more handsome than him. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3551 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6674,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/19\/bilal-from-slave-to-master\/","url_meta":{"origin":3269,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Freedom: Bilal, from our slave to our master","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 19, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, used to say, \u201cAbu Bakr is our master and he emancipated our master,\u201d meaning Bilal. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3754 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u0646 \u062c\u0627\u0628\u0631 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064f\u00a0\u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u064a\u064e\u0642\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0623\u064e\u0628\u064f\u0648 \u0628\u064e\u0643\u0652\u0631\u064d \u0633\u064e\u064a\u0650\u0651\u062f\u064f\u0646\u064e\u0627 \u0648\u064e\u0623\u064e\u0639\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0642\u064e \u0633\u064e\u064a\u0650\u0651\u062f\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0646\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13481,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/10\/hasan-ibn-ali-makes-peace\/","url_meta":{"origin":3269,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Hasan: The Prophet\u2019s grandson Hasan ibn Ali makes peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakrah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThis grandson of mine is a master. Perhaps Allah will reconcile two groups of Muslims through him.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2557 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0628\u064e\u0643\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3269","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp